{"tid":573131,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黃子華7月初再上紅館開棟篤笑, 預開逾15場","createTime":"2018-02-26T07:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T05:44:02.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1945c3fc678e7d602df37f18473ccbd80456da9d","tid":573131,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180226/57876671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57876671&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp11y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=cfb2b2f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180226%2F57876671&h=2a86aa47\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180226/57876671</a><br />\n<br />\n【闊別棟篤笑三年半】黃子華7月初再上紅館開騷 預開逾15場<br />\n<br />\n15,498<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0226 14:45<br />\n<br />\n子華神棟篤笑，返嚟喇，F5制又要ready!隔咗三年半，大家又可以再次叫「回水」同「除褲」。<br />\n<br />\n子華今年7月開騷，一直被指係電影「票房毒藥」嘅黃子華，憑住賀歲片《棟篤特工》大翻身，開畫截至噚日，本港累積票房約3,748萬港元，連同澳門票房，累積票房合共將衝上4千萬元，一洗頹氣，實行再戲院旺到紅館。<br />\n<br />\n據知子華神今年7月初到月中，喺紅館搞棟篤笑，有指預計開15至18場，主辦機構尚未公佈，但子華神忠粉喺網上熱烈討論點撲飛。<br />\n<br />\n子華神自1990年首次喺文化中心搞棟篤笑《娛樂圈血肉史》，將歡樂帶畀觀眾，其後差不多隔年有舉行，2010年殺入紅館，上一次係2014年喺紅館搞《唔黐線唔正常》，搞棟篤笑28年來，喺全球開過逾350場棟篤笑，於同年子華宣告封咪暫別棟篤笑，有感現時香港好陌生，諗好多嘢已經笑唔出。<br />\n<br />\n直至前年，子華都只係孖同陳法拉喺灣仔演藝做舞台劇《前度》，今年先再次正式開騷，雖然未正式宣佈開騷，但網上已有撲飛潮，子華為免粉絲被騙，日前喺facebook作出呼籲：「鑑於近日有個別網站流傳能代訂黃子華2018棟篤笑門票，子華及本會為避免有任何人仕受騙而招致損失，現特別公告此並非官方授權售票網站。」"},{"pid":"0369bb21e9164f1ee7a25b3982316159b5a1e8c7","tid":573131,"uid":30604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"咩事咁錢緊"},{"pid":"82c291ebc0afb7e540f74d11170ab790b3d0d1ce","tid":573131,"uid":52215,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:34:08.000Z","msg":"通常黃子華做緊棟篤笑<br />\n個輪個巿道都唔好"},{"pid":"9fb53dc2895943217f8e6c5af3460d1fa1f28097","tid":573131,"uid":42820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"有回塘feel。。。"},{"pid":"94b9a2ea1befaece4dc4e646d26d72eba68c4cfe","tid":573131,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"據知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nconfirm 左再算啦"},{"pid":"b6d8dc77541970df39e6ca7ee5d39fff8d7ebaae","tid":573131,"uid":33719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fb53dc2895943217f8e6c5af3460d1fa1f28097","tid":573131,"uid":42820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"有回塘feel。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"拾下拾下,無炭用之後回緊塘好耐"},{"pid":"1d714cb515d12855afedd68d66bc46049962e382","tid":573131,"uid":17905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"已經CONFIRM 了<br />\n演出日期：2018年7月6日至22日<br />\n演出地點：香港體育館（紅館）<br />\n演出時間：晚上8時15分開始<br />\n票價：HK$880 / HK$680 / HK$480 / HK$380 / HK$280"},{"pid":"186e5df3f717841f955cc7e9bd597a214dfc77dc","tid":573131,"uid":2333,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"今次個現場肯定好多人<br />\n<br />\n懶好笑咁大叫<br />\n回水 同埋 除褲<br />\n<br />\n比錢買難受"},{"pid":"771aa23b7dc22baa750b27d91c512b2dd59778a2","tid":573131,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d714cb515d12855afedd68d66bc46049962e382","tid":573131,"uid":17905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"已經CONFIRM 了<br />\n演出日期：2018年7月6日至22日<br />\n演出地點：香港體育館（紅館）<br />\n演出時間：晚上8時15分開始<br />\n票價：HK$880 / HK$680 / HK$480 / HK$380 / HK$280"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"有冇咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b58c766ed4f591413bb7e5442376b43be52bf02","tid":573131,"uid":17905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"771aa23b7dc22baa750b27d91c512b2dd597